flowchart TD
    A[User opens Service Request Form] --> B[Submit request]
    B --> C[ServiceRequestController@store]
    C --> D[Generate Reference Code SRF-...]
    D --> E[Status = Pending]
    E --> F[User gets tracking link and reference code]

    F --> G[Track Your Request page]
    G --> H{Request chat with admin?}
    H -- No --> I[Wait for status updates]
    H -- Yes --> J[requestTrackChat]
    J --> K[contact_chat_status = pending]

    K --> L[Admin notification bell or panel]
    L --> M[Open request in Admin Edit page]
    M --> N{Admin decision}
    N -- Accept --> O[decideChatRequest accepted]
    N -- Reject --> P[decideChatRequest rejected]

    O --> Q[Chat enabled]
    Q --> R[Requestor postTrackMessage]
    Q --> S[Admin postAdminMessage]
    R --> T[Messages polling endpoints]
    S --> T

    P --> U[Chat hidden and messages cleared]

    I --> V[Admin updateStatus]
    V --> W{New status}
    W -- Checking --> X[checking_at set]
    W -- Approved --> Y[approved_at plus completed_at set]
    W -- Rejected --> Z[rejected_at plus completed_at set]

    Y --> AA[Move to Archive view]
    Z --> AA

    subgraph Dashboard
      AB[DashboardController@index]
      AC[Counts total pending approved rejected]
      AD[Recent requests and recent chat requests]
      AB --> AC --> AD
    end
